    "name": "Space Trash Scavenger: Prologue",
    "steam_appid": 2135820,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2135820/extras/52ec699eddc53d04e976ba9818e3cef1.avif?t=1686150605\" width=600 height=300 /></span><br><strong>In the 31st century, Space Trash Scavengers roam the cosmos, risking their lives for riches amongst the debris of a galactic war.</strong><br><br>This is the Prologue for Space Trash Scavenger, offering a free introduction to the upcoming interstellar, open-world sandbox.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2135820/extras/84af510114f453dca78fc8e638209b9e.poster.avif?t=1686150605\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2135820/extras/84af510114f453dca78fc8e638209b9e.webm?t=1686150605\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2135820/extras/84af510114f453dca78fc8e638209b9e.mp4?t=1686150605\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>It's day one on the job working for the galaxy’s number one waste disposal firm and space trash is your main resource. <br><br>Gain access to derelict outposts and space wrecks. Prise open maintenance panels, loot abandoned cargo or strip components off spaceship hulls.<br><br>Recycle your haul into raw materials, or trade it at the Trash Exchange.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2135820/extras/ae9fe2936e51c00941e044cd091fd2b3.poster.avif?t=1686150605\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2135820/extras/ae9fe2936e51c00941e044cd091fd2b3.webm?t=1686150605\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2135820/extras/ae9fe2936e51c00941e044cd091fd2b3.mp4?t=1686150605\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Build your Space Rig - a 3D raft with artificial gravity, power, trash processing, farming and defense. Craft the everyday food, fuel, weapons, ammo and space suit upgrades you’ll need to survive.<br><br>In space there is no up or down! Expand your base in any direction for the most efficient layout. Then use your jump drive to voyage to new salvage sectors.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2135820/extras/7772475ac101ef0881efeb4b03df630e.poster.avif?t=1686150605\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2135820/extras/7772475ac101ef0881efeb4b03df630e.webm?t=1686150605\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2135820/extras/7772475ac101ef0881efeb4b03df630e.mp4?t=1686150605\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>You’re not alone amid the wreckage. Watch out for alien bot patrols on your scavenging runs and defend your Space Rig from base attacks.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2135820/extras/b87bd106161dd6e0ad1c260cd9603446.poster.avif?t=1686150605\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2135820/extras/b87bd106161dd6e0ad1c260cd9603446.webm?t=1686150605\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2135820/extras/b87bd106161dd6e0ad1c260cd9603446.mp4?t=1686150605\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Circumnavigate tiny asteroids, fly between abandoned outposts and board derelict spaceships as they orbit the system.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2135820/extras/41f5bf831143bd2720bec0692e454bd6.webp?t=1686150605\" width=600 height=50 /></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Use your jump drive to travel to new salvage zones. Each one is a procedurally generated, dynamic and ever-changing open world.<br></li><li>Extended tech tree to expand your Space Rig and upgrade your weapons and suit.<br></li><li>Loads more enemy types, drawn in ever bigger numbers as your operation expands.<br></li><li>Complete quests for ScavX or NPCs for rewards.<br></li><li>New spacewrecks and outposts to explore.</li></ul><br>We'll be adding more and more to Space Trash Scavenger, so be sure to wishlist and follow for updates! Join our discord (linked to the right) if you'd like to help beta test the game.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2135820/extras/aab2a0298480268fd7454374e70991a5.poster.avif?t=1686150605\" width=600 height=164 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2135820/extras/aab2a0298480268fd7454374e70991a5.webm?t=1686150605\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2135820/extras/aab2a0298480268fd7454374e70991a5.mp4?t=1686150605\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
